==>Todays problem: Program to print Sum of elements in the array and also checks Average of that particular elements 

==>Solution: 
Here this problem is simple and I have implemented with simple logic using Arrays concept.

==>TestCases:
The elements should not float type,String type.

==>Sample Input:
Enter array elements in the array:
20
40
60
80
100

==>Output:
Array elements:
20
40
60
80
100
 Addition 300
 average 60.0
 
